Safety Analysis
✅ All 26 repositories are safe with Priming Page=100:
•	Largest message: 200 KB (Auctions) = 0.15% of 16 MB term buffer limit
•	All messages fit within 2 MB socket buffers
•	Maximum 25 fragments per message (excellent fragmentation efficiency)
•	No risk of exceeding Aeron limits
Risks and Mitigations
Risk	Mitigation
Messages exceed term buffer (16 MB)	Page size 100 creates max 200 KB messages (0.15% of limit)
Socket buffer congestion	2 MB buffers support up to 1 MB messages; largest is 200 KB
MTU mismatch in network path	AWS VPC natively supports MTU 9001 (jumbo frames)
	
 
